OL,3,CMissed appointments and lost
OL,4,Clivelihoods in Scotland's ferry crisis
OL,6,FIslanders and passengers have been
OL,7,Fstranded on the Isle of Arran with
OL,8,Fferries cancelled and services
OL,9,Fstruggling, as ITV News Scotland
OL,10,FReporter Vanessa Taaffe reports
OL,12,FWords by ITV News Scotland Reporter
OL,13,FVanessa Taaffe and ITV News Producer
OL,14,FDaniel Boal
OL,16,FScotland's islanders face weeks of
OL,17,Fdisruption and delays as a beleaguered
OL,18,Fferry service struggles to cope.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
