OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775571066
OL,3,CMissed appointments and lost
OL,4,Clivelihoods in Scotland's ferry crisis
OL,6,FVirtually every Scottish island has
OL,7,Fbeen cut off in recent weeks as state-
OL,8,Fowned operator CalMac warns of further
OL,9,Fdisruption to the beleaguered and
OL,10,Fageing ferry fleet.
OL,12,FThe delays and disruption alongside
OL,13,Fplanned maintenance of vessels have
OL,14,Fseen the issue dominate the political
OL,15,Fagenda, becoming a major election
OL,16,Fissue as voters prepare to head to the
OL,17,Fpolls in the Holyrood elections next
OL,18,Fmonth.
OL,20,FWho is to blame for Scotland's ferry
OL,21,Ffiasco?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775571066
OL,3,CMissed appointments and lost
OL,4,Clivelihoods in Scotland's ferry crisis
OL,6,FThe Isle of Arran is nestled off the
OL,7,Fwest coast of Scotland. The ferry is a
OL,8,Flifeline service for islanders and the
OL,9,Fthousands of visitors who help to
OL,10,Fsupport the island's economy.
OL,12,FEverything from food and fuel to
OL,13,Fhealthcare and tourism is tied to a
OL,14,Freliable connection to mainland
OL,15,FScotland. But that connection is
OL,16,Fbecoming increasingly fragile.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775571066
OL,3,CMissed appointments and lost
OL,4,Clivelihoods in Scotland's ferry crisis
OL,6,FThe Glen Sannox, the delayed and over-
OL,7,Fbudget ferry that services the Arran
OL,8,Froute, has been plagued with technical
OL,9,Fissues and breakdowns after being in
OL,10,Fservice for little more than a year.
OL,12,FIt was taken out of action again on
OL,13,FTuesday after suffering another engine
OL,14,Ffault, just a week after returning to
OL,15,Fservice.
OL,17,FCalMac suspended sailings until at
OL,18,Fleast 1pm on Tuesday, due to a
OL,19,F"recurring technical issue" with its
OL,20,Fport engine fuel pump.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
