OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775571066
OL,3,CMissed appointments and lost
OL,4,Clivelihoods in Scotland's ferry crisis
OL,6,FIslanders are still waiting for its
OL,7,Fsister ship, the Glen Rosa, to join
OL,8,Fthe fleet.
OL,10,FAn ageing fleet, repeated
OL,11,Fcancellations and delays to long-
OL,12,Fpromised upgrades have left many cut
OL,13,Foff - not just from the mainland, but
OL,14,Ffrom decision-makers in Holyrood.
OL,16,FElizabeth Bell relies on the ferry to
OL,17,Fattend vital medical appointments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775571066
OL,3,CMissed appointments and lost
OL,4,Clivelihoods in Scotland's ferry crisis
OL,6,FShe's spent more than a decade on a
OL,7,Fwaiting list for a specialist
OL,8,Fneurological diagnosis. As her health
OL,9,Fdeteriorated over that time, her
OL,10,Fcondition means she is now unable to
OL,11,Fwalk.
OL,13,FAs a wheelchair user, her ferry
OL,14,Fjourney often requires "military
OL,15,Fplanning".
OL,17,F"It's not an easy task when you're a
OL,18,Fwheelchair user," she said.
OL,26,@vD@XOUwD@IO]yD@AOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775571066
OL,3,CMissed appointments and lost
OL,4,Clivelihoods in Scotland's ferry crisis
OL,6,F"If I'm to go over to the mainland, it
OL,7,Fis a major planning. The night before,
OL,8,Fyou are packing an overnight bag every
OL,9,Ftime, making sure you've got all your
OL,10,Fmeds with you. One of the big issues
OL,11,Fis if you do end up getting stuck on
OL,12,Fthe mainland as a wheelchair user,
OL,13,Fdon't have your carers with you."
OL,15,FWhen Elizabeth finally secured an
OL,16,Fappointment with a new specialist
OL,17,Fafter a six-month wait, she booked her
OL,18,Fferry immediately.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775571066
OL,3,CMissed appointments and lost
OL,4,Clivelihoods in Scotland's ferry crisis
OL,6,FBut it was cancelled, and she missed
OL,7,Fthe appointment. She was then placed
OL,8,Fback on the waiting list.
OL,10,F"It's incredibly frustrating," she
OL,11,Fsaid. "They can only do so much over
OL,12,Fthe phone. For something like this,
OL,13,Fthey have to physically examine you."
OL,15,FWith the Scottish election
OL,16,Fapproaching, she believes island
OL,17,Fcommunities are being overlooked.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
