OL,3,CMissed appointments and lost
OL,4,Clivelihoods in Scotland's ferry crisis
OL,6,FThe SNP have been in power in Scotland
OL,7,Ffor 19 years and in charge of
OL,8,Fdelivering the vessels for the
OL,9,FScottish islands.
OL,11,FElizabeth feels let down by the party,
OL,12,Fsaying they've not done enough for
OL,13,Fisland communities like hers.
OL,15,F"The islands have been forgotten about
OL,16,Fin a lot of ways," she said. "We have
OL,17,Fthings like The Islands Bill and The
OL,18,FIsland Plans, all of these fancy
OL,19,Fthings being put in (to policy), but
OL,20,Fnone of it's being implemented."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30710
